library(COVID19)
# Examining situation in USA

## To retrieve citation and metadata of the data sources see ?covid19cite. To hide this message use 'verbose = FALSE'.
ggplot(covid_us, aes(x = date , y = confirmed)) +
geom_line() +
facet_wrap(~id)

# Examining situation in USA
covid_us %>% dplyr::filter(id %in%
c("USA, New York",
"USA, Arizona",
"USA, Utah",
"USA, Florida")
) %>%
ggplot(aes(x = date , y = confirmed, color = id)) +
geom_line()
